The police&#8217;s Nqobile Gwala says the man threatened to kill his child if she told anyone about the crime. JOHANNESBURG A 39-year-old man has been sentenced to life behind bars for raping his 12-year-old daughter.The police s Nqobile Gwala says the man threatened to kill his child if she told anyone about the crime.He says the child confided in her grandmother - who then opened a case. The father was sentenced to life imprisonment by the Umlazi Regional Court. The sentencing came after we celebrated National Child Protection Week. We encourage our community to protect and defend our children. 